{{Infobox settlement | name = Vila Madalena | native_name = | native_name_lang = | settlement_type = | image_skyline = Rua Heitor Penteado SP.jpg | imagesize = 250px | image_alt = | image_caption = Rua Heitor Penteado in Vila Madalena | nickname = | coordinates = {{coord|-23.5525|-46.691389|display=inline,title}} | subdivision_type = [[List of sovereign states|Country]] | subdivision_name = {{flag|Brazil}} | subdivision_type1 = [[Regions of Brazil|Region]] | subdivision_name1 = [[Southeast Region, Brazil|Southeast]] | subdivision_type2 = [[States of Brazil|State]] | subdivision_name2 = [[File:Bandeira do Estado de São Paulo.svg|border|22px]] [[São Paulo (state)|São Paulo]] | subdivision_type3 = [[Municipalities of Brazil|Municipality]] | subdivision_name3 = [[File:São Paulo City flag.svg|border|22px]] [[São Paulo]] | subdivision_type4 = [[Subdivisions of the City of São Paulo#Administrative Zones|Administrative Zone]] | subdivision_name4 = [[West Zone of São Paulo|West]] | subdivision_type5 = [[Subprefecture]] | subdivision_name5 = [[Subprefecture of Pinheiros|Pinheiros]] | subdivision_type6 = [[District]] | subdivision_name6 = [[Pinheiros (district of São Paulo)|Pinheiros]] | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} '''Vila Madalena''' is an [[upper middle class]] neighborhood of the [[Pinheiros (district of São Paulo)|Pinheiros]] district in the western<ref name="monocle Ricardo Moreno" /> part of the city of [[São Paulo]], [[Brazil]]. The neighborhood is known for its bustling nightlife<ref>"The Economist Magazine Cities Guide: São Paulo". ''[[The Economist]]''.</ref> and its history as a center of São Paulo [[Bohemianism|bohemian]] culture and art. The neighborhood is filled with dozens of art galleries and studios, an eclectic mix of restaurants and bars and a series of [[graffiti]]-covered streets and alleys, and is attracting young professionals.<ref name="monocle Ricardo Moreno">{{cite web | url= http://monocle.com/magazine/issues/70/vila-madalena/ | title= Vila Madalena—São Paulo | last= Moreno | first= Ricardo | publisher= [[Monocle magazine]] | date= February 2014 }}</ref>
