{{Orphan|date=November 2015}}
'''Zhunagbiao''' (裝裱) is a Chinese specialized [[Picture frame|framing]] method for paintings and calligraphy on [[rice paper]]s. Materials include: coloured papers, fabrics, threads, wooden sticks, glue and so on.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://baike.baidu.com/view/21018.htm |title=百度一下，你就知道 |publisher=Baike.baidu.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-31}}</ref>
